					Table 10 - Sacred Law: Law 5: Item a
				-
					-
						A dead person's bones shall not be collected that one may make a second
						funeral.
					-
				-
					Table 10 - Sacred Law: Law 5: Item b
				-
					-
						An exception is for death in battle and on foreign soil.
					-
